node.person.name: Thomas Petersen
node.areas_of_interest_freeform:
We like to have skin in the game and get in very early which means that we get involved with two different types of founders.
1) Founders who have raised capital and are looking for a venture studio to help them design and develop their product.
2) Founders who haven't raised any capital and are looking for someone to partner with to help build their product. 
We are industry agnostic. We like to keep things simple.
